{
  "id": "RAW_9513fc59",
  "title": "Veo 3.1 从素材到视频：更强的连贯性、创造力和控制力",
  "url": "https://deepmind.google/blog/veo-3-1-ingredients-to-video-more-consistency-creativity-and-control/",
  "date": "2026-01-13 17:00:01",
  "author": "Ricky Wong",
  "siteName": "Google DeepMind Blog",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2026-01-13T17:00:01.082354+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$439443497$-->\n    <span width=\"14px\"> \n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg> \n    </span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"jd4lc\" class=\"drop-cap\">Today, <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/models/veo/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Veo</a> is getting more expressive, with improvements that help you create more fun, creative, high-quality videos based on ingredient images, built directly for the mobile format. We’re excited to bring new creative possibilities for everyone from casual storytellers to professional filmmakers.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"16ohq\">We’re releasing:</p>\n     <ol>\n      <li data-block-key=\"2216u\"><b>Improvements to Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video,</b> our capability that lets you create videos based on reference images. This update makes videos more expressive and creative, even with simple prompts</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"1lo7k\"><b>Native vertical outputs for Ingredients to Video (portrait mode)</b> to power mobile-first, short-form video creation</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"fpr8f\"><b>State-of-the-art upscaling to 1080p and 4K resolution</b> for high-fidelity production workflows</li>\n     </ol>\n     <p data-block-key=\"34t51\">Whether you are looking for livelier movement, better control over visual elements or broadcast-ready resolution, these updates give you the tools to bring your vision to life. These updates are launching in the Gemini app, YouTube, Flow, Google Vids, the Gemini API and Vertex AI.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"jd4lc\">Improvements to Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video</h2>\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"1d0bj\">Turn ingredient images into fun, shareable clips</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"7ptpb\">Even with short prompts, you can generate dynamic and engaging videos based on ingredient images. You’ll now see richer dialogue and storytelling, making your videos feel more alive and expressive.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"3\" thumbnail-alt=\"Veo compilation video\" video-id=\"xJngjnLZ_ZI\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"xJngjnLZ_ZI\" data-index-id=\"3\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/xJngjnLZ_ZI/default.webp\" alt=\"Veo compilation video\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/xJngjnLZ_ZI/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/xJngjnLZ_ZI/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"><!----></uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \"><!----></uni-icon-component><!--?lit$439443497$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"jd4lc\">Maintain identity consistency for your characters</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"12l8a\">Identity consistency is better than ever with Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video. Keep your characters looking the same even as the setting changes, making it easier to tell a full narrative by having the same character appear across multiple scenes.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"5\" thumbnail-alt=\"Veo 3.1 compilation\" video-id=\"9a60zH_oye4\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"9a60zH_oye4\" data-index-id=\"5\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/9a60zH_oye4/default.webp\" alt=\"Veo 3.1 compilation\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/9a60zH_oye4/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/9a60zH_oye4/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"><!----></uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \"><!----></uni-icon-component><!--?lit$439443497$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"jd4lc\">Achieve background and object consistency</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"90cf1\">Control the scene by maintaining the integrity of your setting and the objects within it. You can also reuse an object, backgrounds or textures across scenes.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"7\" thumbnail-alt=\"Veo compilation\" video-id=\"70HPDPtJNTQ\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"70HPDPtJNTQ\" data-index-id=\"7\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/70HPDPtJNTQ/default.webp\" alt=\"Veo compilation\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/70HPDPtJNTQ/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/70HPDPtJNTQ/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"><!----></uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \"><!----></uni-icon-component><!--?lit$439443497$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"jd4lc\">Seamlessly blend textures, characters and objects</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"cb9av\">Combine disparate elements — like characters, objects, textures and stylized backgrounds — into a cohesive, high-impact clip.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"9\" thumbnail-alt=\"Veo compilation\" video-id=\"HuVYtBCx8IU\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"HuVYtBCx8IU\" data-index-id=\"9\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/HuVYtBCx8IU/default.webp\" alt=\"Veo compilation\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/HuVYtBCx8IU/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/HuVYtBCx8IU/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"><!----></uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \"><!----></uni-icon-component><!--?lit$439443497$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"280he\"><b>Pro tip:</b> use the new <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/models/gemini-image/pro/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Nano Banana Pro</a> (Gemini 3 Pro Image) in the <a href=\"http://gemini.google.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini app</a> or <a href=\"http://flow.google/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Flow</a> to create your ingredient images, which you can then use to create stunning videos with Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"280he\">Create high-fidelity visuals with upgraded capabilities</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"3reqg\">With Veo 3.1’s new capabilities, we are introducing mobile-optimized outputs and professional-grade quality options.</p>\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"1dhff\">Native vertical outputs for Ingredients to Video</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"6c4um\">For the first time, \"Ingredients to Video\" supports generating videos in a native 9:16 aspect ratio. Whether you are creating for YouTube Shorts or other platforms, you can now produce high-quality, full-screen vertical storytelling without cropping or quality loss.</p>\n     <h3 data-block-key=\"65oh0\">State-of-the-art upscaling to 1080p and 4K resolution</h3>\n     <p data-block-key=\"3lniq\">Generate videos 1080p and 4K with state-of-the-art upscaling. Our improved 1080p resolution offers a sharper, cleaner video perfect for editing. For even more detail, choose 4K to capture rich textures and stunning clarity — ideal for high-end productions and large screens.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"12\" thumbnail-alt=\"Veo 3.1 compilation\" video-id=\"uP9f0aYy6as\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"uP9f0aYy6as\" data-index-id=\"12\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/uP9f0aYy6as/default.webp\" alt=\"Veo 3.1 compilation\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/uP9f0aYy6as/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/uP9f0aYy6as/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"><!----></uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \"><!----></uni-icon-component><!--?lit$439443497$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"280he\">Try these updates today</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2f7f7\">Across our products and services, you can now access these new capabilities tailored to your workflow:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"4dlbn\"><b>Consumers and creators:</b> We are bringing Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video directly to <a href=\"https://support.google.com/s/community/forum/659278/thread/400398403\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube Shorts and the YouTube Create app</a> for the first time. You can also try the enhanced Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video and portrait mode for Veo in the <a href=\"http://gemini.google.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini app</a> starting today.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"1rql4\"><b>Professional and enterprise workflows:</b> The enhanced Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video and native vertical format support are rolling out to <a href=\"http://flow.google/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Flow</a>, the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/video\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini API</a>, <a href=\"https://console.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/studio/media/video\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vertex AI</a>, and <a href=\"http://docs.google.com/videos/create?usp=blog\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google Vids</a>, with 1080p and 4K resolution options also available on Flow, the API, and Vertex AI.</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"sswa0\">Verify videos in the Gemini app</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"9rd55\">We’re committed to providing tools to make it easier to determine if content is AI-generated. This is why videos generated by Google’s tools are embedded with our imperceptible <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/models/synthid/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SynthID</a> digital watermark.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"9fvtn\">In December we expanded our powerful verification tool in the <a href=\"http://gemini.google.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini app</a> to include video. You can now upload a video and simply ask if it was generated with Google AI. This builds on our existing image verification tools, helping to foster a more transparent ecosystem for everyone.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"15\" thumbnail-alt=\"SynthID video\" video-id=\"hzkG07u8ITU\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"hzkG07u8ITU\" data-index-id=\"15\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/hzkG07u8ITU/default.webp\" alt=\"SynthID video\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/hzkG07u8ITU/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/hzkG07u8ITU/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"><!----></uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \"><!----></uni-icon-component><!--?lit$439443497$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Veo 3.1 Ingredients to Video: More consistency, creativity and control&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"280he\">You can find out more about how we’re increasing transparency in AI content with SynthID in our <a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/ai/verify-google-ai-videos-gemini-app/\">blog post</a>.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google DeepMind 的 Veo 3.1 '从素材到视频' 功能迎来重大更新，提供改进的连贯性、创造力、移动端优化的竖屏格式以及高达 4K 的分辨率，同时还具备 AI 内容透明度功能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google DeepMind 的 Veo 3.1 '从素材到视频' 功能迎来重大更新，提供改进的连贯性、创造力、移动端优化的竖屏格式以及高达 4K 的分辨率，同时还具备 AI 内容透明度功能。",
  "summary": "本文宣布了 Google DeepMind 的 Veo 3.1 '从素材到视频' 功能的重大更新，这是一个从参考图像生成视频的生成式 AI 模型。主要改进包括增强角色、背景和物体的表现力、创造力和连贯性，即使使用简单提示词也能实现更丰富的故事叙述。此次更新还引入了原生竖屏（9:16）视频输出，针对移动优先的短视频内容进行了优化，并提供最先进的 1080p 和 4K 分辨率升级功能，适用于专业制作工作流。这些新功能正在整合到 Google 的整个生态系统中，包括 YouTube Shorts、Gemini 应用、Flow、Google Vids、Gemini API 和 Vertex AI。此外，Google 重申其对 AI 内容透明度的承诺，通过在其工具生成的视频中嵌入不可感知的 SynthID 数字水印，并在 Gemini 应用中扩展视频验证功能。",
